{"type": "article", "id": 20302, "title": "带夹子的台灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-06T07:00:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000936uZfJCMcmhkt2RbXv.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一个带夹子的台灯，它有一个有趣的比例。灯体是细长的，有 18 英寸，可以弯曲，圆柱形的灯头却显得短小，只有 6 英寸，是用木头做的，对比之下有种探寻的意味，有点类似于外星人。因为灯体细长，灯光的方向和角度也很大的调整空间，很灵活。灯头有多种颜色，售价 145 美元，<a href=\"http://www.gagan-design.com/products/peliclamp-desk-lamp\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606000934ORfpnCz5H04adyEu.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606000935dh2vUoR7yG9a4tPS.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606000935m4DLnu5sil3o2RhK.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606000936Metc3suRHwWFI0lX.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}